{"tid":2312391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國對中國統戰部部分官員實施簽證限制","createTime":"2020-12-05T01:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T02:08:13.000Z","uid":278587,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d41c5116152d9272c04f59b890fb884f606b206b","tid":2312391,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T01:59:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=415427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415427&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=ecab49fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415427&h=7512f6ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=415427</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國對中國統戰部部分官員和相關人員實施簽證限制。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧發表聲明，指控中國共產黨統戰部脅迫和霸凌反對北京政策的人士，會依據《移民與國籍法》禁止他們入境美國，聲明又指控統戰部資助海外組織使用暴力，或透過脅迫公開私人資訊等手段，打壓學界、商界、公民團體，特別是涉及新疆、西藏等少數民族的組織，又試圖在美國拉攏支持者，延續當局的威權及自身的政策主張。<br />\n<br />\n美國早前收緊對中國共產黨黨員和家屬的簽證政策，外交部發言人華春瑩認為非常可笑、荒謬，也非常可悲。"},{"pid":"779c4205a30f407191a3fcf6dfa4e196c99a4f96","tid":2312391,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T02:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b0b0ff0924c0509904a60581b2749c4258cb6d","tid":2312391,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T02:08:13.000Z","msg":"咁鐘意借自由世界玩超限戰呀啦"}]}